<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px
      auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden; border-top: 5px solid #8254f8; }
      .wrapper { padding: 20px; } .banner { height: 50px; background: #ffffff;
      color: #8254f8; text-align: center; display: flex; justify-content:
      center; align-items: center; font-size: 40px; gap: 10px; padding: 20px;
      font-weight: bold; } h2 { color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px; } p { color:
      #555; line-height: 1.6; } strong { color: #8254f8; } .button { display:
      inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; font-size: 18px; color: #fff;
      background-color: #8254f8; text-align: center; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; transition: background-color 0.3s; }
      .button:hover { background-color: #6a3fcf; } .footer { margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left; font-size: 12px; color: #666; } .highlight {
      background-color: #e7e7ff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; } .list {
      margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px; } .list li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <section class='banner'>
        <img
          src='https://discoursefy-public-bucket.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/logo+h.png'
          alt='Discoursefy Logo'
          style='height: 50px'
        />
      </section>
      <div class='wrapper'>
        <h2>
          Your Friend
          {{referrerName}}
          Invites You to Unlock Career Opportunities with Discoursefy!
        </h2>
        <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
        <p>
          On behalf of your friend
          {{referrerName}}, we’d like to invite you to
          <strong>Discoursefy</strong>—the perfect platform to help you stand
          out to recruiters and unlock new career opportunities.
        </p>

        <div class='highlight'>
          <strong>Why Discoursefy?</strong>
          <ul class='list'>
            <li>Enhance your skills and showcase them to top recruiters.</li>
            <li>Get noticed with an in-depth view of your expertise.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>
          <strong>Recruiter-Focused Performance Profiles</strong><br />
          Our platform tracks your progress in real-time, giving recruiters a
          comprehensive view of your strengths, adaptability, and leadership
          skills.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Stand Out with Real-World Problem Solving</strong><br />
          From Data Structures & Algorithms to C++ and beyond, you'll sharpen
          your skills with hands-on challenges that prove your worth.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Soft Skills That Matter</strong><br />
          Highlight essential soft skills like communication, passion, and
          adaptability, so you're more than just a resume.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Join Discoursefy Today!</strong><br />
          Start building your profile, get noticed by recruiters, and take
          control of your career growth. Your journey to new opportunities
          starts here.
        </p>

        <div>
          <a href='https://app.discoursefy.com' class='button'>Join Now</a>
        </div>

        <p>
          Looking forward to seeing you achieve your career goals on
          Discoursefy!
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Discoursefy Team</p>
        <p class='footer'>Learn. Evaluate. Get Noticed.<br />Discoursefy</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>